{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji30.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给文炳璋的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给文炳璋的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年10月10日）炳璋同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月五日来信收到，谢谢你。乡里来人说，你家生活情况有了一些改善。你可安心在军队工作。此复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺祝进步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十月十日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]文炳璋（1920一1973），湖南省韶山市大坪乡大坪村唐家（当时属湘乡）人，毛泽东的表侄。文炳璋当时在中国人民解放军广东军区防空司令部通讯连工作，1954年转业，后在北京合成纤维厂工作。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1951,"month":10,"day":10}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":523,"page_end":523},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}